result:
<v-card>
    <v-toolbar dark color="purple">
        <v-toolbar-title>Results</v-toolbar-title>
        <v-spacer></v-spacer>
        <v-toolbar-items>
            <v-btn dark text @click="$parent.$parent.$parent.dialog = false">Close</v-btn>
        </v-toolbar-items>
    </v-toolbar>
    <v-content>
        <v-layout justify-center align-center row>
            <v-flex xs6>
                {{results[0].q}}
            </v-flex>
            <v-flex xs6>
                {{results[0].a}}
            </v-flex>
        </v-layout>
    </v-content>
</v-card>
